s="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://www.thunderbird.net/zh-CN/"   title="邮箱客户端：Thunderbird"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>邮箱客户端：Thunderbird</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://www.videolan.org/vlc/index.zh_CN.html"   title="播放器：VLC"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>播放器：VLC</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu orange larger" href="https://geekuninstaller.com/"   title="卸载工具：Geek"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>卸载工具：Geek</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu orange larger" href="https://www.internetdownloadmanager.com/"   title="下载器：IDM"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>下载器：IDM</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu orange larger" href="https://www.voidtools.com/zh-cn/"   title="搜索文件：everything"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>搜索文件：everything</span></a><p><a href="https://www.videolan.org/vlc/index.zh_CN.html">https://www.videolan.org/vlc/index.zh_CN.html</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
